    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "it sounds really intense lol. i've heard people say it's only a problem if you drink a lot though. like, if i just have a tiny bit tucked into my meal, would the reaction really be that bad? it's just a social thing and i don't want to be the only one not drinking.",
