      "content": "Even a \"tiny bit\" of wine while on metronidazole is a risk, and I advise against it entirely. The reaction isn't just about the *amount* you drink; it's about the interaction between the alcohol and the drug. To ensure your treatment works perfectly and you don't end up feeling awful, you must abstain completely. Your health is more important than any dinner party etiquette.",
